headline: WireX Systems and Brown & Brown Announce Strategic Collaboration to Advance Cyber Risk Management and Insurance Outcomes
summary: WireX Systems is pleased to announce a strategic collaboration with Brown & Brown to combine its industry-leading cybersecurity solutions with Brown & Brown Risk Solutions' evidence-based risk identification, quantification, and financing process to deliver enhanced risk management and insurance outcomes for their customers.
